        <Parent_String>quartz porphyry [300011238], rhyolite [300011211], acid igneous rock [300011180], igneous rock by composition: chemical [300011179], igneous rock by composition [300157789], igneous rock [300011178], rock (inorganic material) [300011692], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
